Package edu.cnm.deepdive.java_learn.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefinitionsFragment
    This class holds the logic for the Definitions game.
    GameFragment
    This class is used to give a common super class to all of the game types for modularity in the code.
    HomeFragment
    This is the landing fragment for when a user first logs in.
    LevelsFragment
    LevelsFragment class allows the user to select between 4 different game levels HighLight, Drag and Drop, Fill in the blank, and Multiple Choice.
    ProfileFragment
    This class is used to display the progress of the user.
